": \"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/sunfox_blue_logo-1-svg.svg\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"datePublished\": \"2024-03-14\"\n}\n<\/script>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1fba79d elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1fba79d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/6.1What-is-a-3-Channel-ECG-Machine-What-is-it-Used-For_-scaled.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-36753\" alt=\"3 channel ecg machine\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/6.1What-is-a-3-Channel-ECG-Machine-What-is-it-Used-For_-scaled.webp 2560w, https:\/\/sunfox.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/6.1What-is-a-3-Channel-ECG-Machine-What-is-it-Used-For_-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/sunfox.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/6.1What-is-a-3-Channel-ECG-Machine-What-is-it-Used-For_-1024x576.webp 1024w, https:\/\/sunfox.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/6.1What-is-a-3-Channel-ECG-Machine-What-is-it-Used-For_-150x84.webp 150w, https:\/\/sunfox.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/6.1What-is-a-3-Channel-ECG-Machine-What-is-it-Used-For_-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/sunfox.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/6.1What-is-a-3-Channel-ECG-Machine-What-is-it-Used-For_-1536x864.webp 1536w, https:\/\/sunfox.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/6.1What-is-a-3-Channel-ECG-Machine-What-is-it-Used-For_-2048x1152.webp 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-206686e e-con-full elementor-hidden-tablet elementor-hidden-mobile e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"206686e\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4abada3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4abada3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Related Article<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9a190bc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9a190bc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/understanding-t-wave-abnormality\/\">Understanding t wave abnormalities symptoms causes and treatment<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/p-wave-ecg-abnormalities-and-their-role-in-cardiac-wellness\/\">P wave ecg abnormalities and their role in cardiac wellness<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/qrs-complex-abnormalities-in-cardiac-health\/\">QRS complex abnormalities: Clarifying ECG Abnormalities for Heart Health<\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ef63da2 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ef63da2\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bb577db e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"bb577db\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-592d644 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"592d644\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><span>Author:- Mr. Ritesh Sharma\n<\/span><\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-558b2660 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"558b2660\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It goes without saying that an <a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/5-common-heart-tests-and-their-diagnostic-insights\/\">electrocardiogram test<\/a> holds great significance in the domain of<a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/comprehensive-cardiac-patient-care-a-guide\/\"> cardiac care<\/a>. The ECG test is performed through various <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/what-is-an-ecg-machine-used-for\/\">ECG machines<\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. One of these machines is a 3 Channel ECG Machine. This machine plays a pivotal part in detecting several heart abnormalities. As it is clear from its name, a 3 Channel ECG Machine records the electrical impulses radiated by the <a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/what-is-the-internal-structure-of-the-human-heart\/\">human heart<\/a> from 3 distinct channels simultaneously. A 3 Channel ECG Machine is the one that stands out because of its balance of functionality and efficiency.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Since a 3 Channel ECG Machine plays such a vital role in the domain of healthcare, it is important for clinicians to be aware of each and every facet of it. Hence, we have crafted this blog. Through this blog, we aim to explain what a 3 channel ECG machine is, how it works, and its primary applications in medical practice. Therefore, both clinicians and general people who have skewed knowledge about an <a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/ecg-full-form\/\">electrocardiogram<\/a> will get worthy information regarding a 3 Channel ECG machine.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0d44c83 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"0d44c83\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-820992e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"820992e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What is a 3 Channel ECG Machine?\n<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-17706c1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"17706c1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As we mentioned earlier that a 3 channel ECG machine is a type of <a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/the-history-of-ecg-innovation\/\">electrocardiograph <\/a>that records electrical signals from<a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/evolution-of-the-heart-explained\/\"> the heart<\/a> across three channels simultaneously. Now, you must know that this is in contrast to the single-channel ECG Machine that only records from one lead at a time. Whereas, this is also quite different from a multi-channel ECG channel that records from more than 3 leads at a time and that too simultaneously.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In a typical ECG setup, multiple <a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/what-are-ecg-electrodes\/\">electrodes<\/a> are placed on the patient\u2019s body at specific points, usually on the chest, arms, and legs. These electrodes detect the electrical activity generated by the heart&#8217;s contractions. The 3 channel ECG machine captures these signals from three leads at a time and presents them in a readable format, either on paper or a digital screen.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-365e3a1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"365e3a1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">How does a 3 Channel ECG Machine Work?\n<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d2ecbe1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d2ecbe1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The working principle of a 3 channel ECG machine is based on detecting the heart&#8217;s electrical impulses and translating them into a visual representation known as an electrocardiogram. Here\u2019s a step-by-step breakdown of its operation:<\/span><\/p><ul><li><b>Electrode Placement:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Electrodes are attached to the patient\u2019s skin at various points, typically involving 10 <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/what-are-ecg-electrodes\/\">ECG electrodes<\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> for a <a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/12-lead-ecg-placement-guide\/\">12-lead ECG<\/a>, which includes limb and chest leads.<\/span><\/li><li><b>Signal Acquisition:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> The electrodes pick up the electrical activity of the heart. In a 3 channel <a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/what-is-an-ecg-machine-used-for\/\">ECG machine<\/a>, three leads (combinations of electrodes) are recorded simultaneously.<\/span><\/li><li><b>Amplification and Filtering: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The electrical signals are often very weak, so the machine amplifies them. It also filters out noise and interference to ensure a clear signal.<\/span><\/li><li><b>Data Conversion:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> The analog signals are converted into digital form for processing.<\/span><\/li><li><b>Display and Print: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The processed signals are then displayed on a screen or printed out on graph paper, showing the heart&#8217;s activity as waveforms.<\/span><\/li><li><b>Interpretation: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These waveforms are analyzed by healthcare professionals to diagnose various heart conditions.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1cf3d79 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"1cf3d79\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-da7ffa0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"da7ffa0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Advantages of a 3 Channel ECG Machine\n<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-46c330a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"46c330a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li><b>Efficiency: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Recording three leads at a time speeds up the process compared to single-channel machines, making it ideal for busy clinical settings.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Accuracy: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">By recording multiple leads simultaneously, it provides a more comprehensive picture of the heart&#8217;s activity, improving diagnostic accuracy.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Portability: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Many 3 channel ECG machines are designed to be compact and <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/spandan-ecg-feature-the-portable-ecg-machine\/\">portable<\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, making them suitable for use in different environments, including clinics, hospitals, and even home visits.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Cost-Effective:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> They offer a balance between functionality and cost, making them a practical choice for many healthcare providers.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1ee4c4c elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"1ee4c4c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5faf3ab elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5faf3ab\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Primary Uses of a 3 Channel ECG Machine\n<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e8c2326 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e8c2326\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Diagnosing Cardiac Conditions:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> The primary use of a 3 channel ECG machine is to diagnose various heart conditions. These include arrhythmias (<a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/understanding-abnormal-ecg-waves-with-spandan-ecg\/\">irregular heartbeats<\/a>), myocardial infarction (<a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/cardiac-arrest-vs-heart-attack\/\">heart attacks<\/a>), and other forms of heart disease. By analyzing the patterns and intervals of the heart&#8217;s electrical activity, physicians can detect abnormalities and initiate appropriate treatments.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Monitoring Heart Health: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For patients with known heart conditions, regular ECG monitoring is essential. A 3 channel ECG machine can be used in routine check-ups to monitor the progress of heart disease and the effectiveness of treatments.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Pre-Surgical Assessments: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Before undergoing surgery, patients often require a thorough evaluation of their <a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/comprehensive-cardiac-patient-care-a-guide\/\">cardiac health<\/a>. ECG is a standard part of pre-surgical assessments to ensure that patients can safely undergo anesthesia and the surgical procedure.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Emergency Diagnosis: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In emergency settings, such as when a patient presents with <a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/gastric-pain-in-chest-vs-cardiac-chest-pain\/\">chest pain<\/a>, a 3 channel ECG machine can provide rapid and essential information to diagnose a<a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/panic-attack-vs-heart-attack\/\"> heart attack<\/a> or other critical conditions.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Fitness Assessments:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Athletes and individuals involved in strenuous physical activities often undergo ECG testing to ensure their hearts are healthy and capable of handling high levels of exertion.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Research and Education:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/what-is-an-ecg-machine-used-for\/\"> ECG machines<\/a>, including 3 channel models, are invaluable tools in medical research and education. They help in studying heart function, developing new treatments, and training healthcare professionals.\u00a0<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d2762fb elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"d2762fb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ea53f14 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ea53f14\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Technological Advancements in 3 Channel ECG Machines\n<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-db6eba7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"db6eba7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Recent advancements have significantly enhanced the capabilities of 3 channel ECG machines:<\/span><\/p><ol><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Digital Integration:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Modern 3 channel ECG machines often come with digital interfaces, allowing seamless integration with electronic health records (EHR) and telemedicine platforms. This facilitates better data management and remote consultations.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Enhanced Signal Processing:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Improvements in signal processing algorithms have led to clearer and more accurate ECG readings, reducing the chances of misdiagnosis.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Wireless and Portable Models:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> The development of wireless and battery-operated models has increased the portability and convenience of 3 channel ECG machines, making them more accessible for home healthcare and emergency services.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>User-Friendly Interfaces: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Newer models come with intuitive interfaces and touchscreen controls, simplifying the operation for healthcare providers and reducing the chances of user error.<\/span><\/li><\/ol><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>In conclusion, a 3-channel ECG machine is the future of healthcare and must be embraced by everyone. By detecting heart abnormalities ranging from <a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/heart-palpitations-are-frequent\/\">heart palpitations<\/a> to <a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/understanding-the-pathophysiology-of-cardiac-arrhythmia\/\">cardiac arrhythmias<\/a> with 3 leads simultaneously, the norms of a <a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/conventional-ecg-machine\/\">conventional ECG<\/a> test are defied for good. For healthcare providers and patients alike, the<a href=\"https:\/\/drcardio.in\/blog\/what-are-the-differences-between-1-3-6-and-12-channel-ecg-machines\/\" rel=\"noopener\"> 3 channel ECG machine<\/a> represents a critical component in the quest for better <a href=\"https:\/\/sunfox.in\/blogs\/10-ways-to-keep-your-heart-healthy\/\">heart health<\/a>.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-22f84d8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"22f84d8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f9f8749 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"f9f8749\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a359fad elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"a359fad\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c1641ba elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"c1641ba\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-294e116 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"294e116\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>